{% block subject '[GRIIDC] DIF Created' %}

{% block body_html %}
    Dear {{ dataManager.firstName }} {{ dataManager.lastName }},<br>
    <br>
    This email is to notify you that a Dataset Information Form (DIF) has been created by {{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName }}. The DIF {{ udi }} has been saved, but has not yet been submitted to the Gulf of Mexico Research Initiative Information and Data Cooperative (GRIIDC) for review and approval. {{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName }} is a member of {{ user.researchGroups | join(', ') }} and the dataset is associated with {{ researchGroup.title }}.<br>
    <br>
    Thank you,<br>
    <br>
    The GRIIDC Team<br>
    <br>
    *You are receiving this email because you are identified as a data manager for a Gulf of Mexico Research Initiative Research Consortium. If you believe you should not be receiving this email please notify <a href="mailto:griidc@gomri.org">griidc@gomri.org</a>.*
{% endblock %}

